“Suddenly I See” by KT Tunstall '70s Simon & Garfunkel style cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Ashley Campbell & Peedy Chavis.
Get The Song: http://pmjlive.com/suddenlyisee | Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ
World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com | PMJ on Spotify: http://pmjlive.com/pmjspotify 

Greetings from our Europe Fall Tour! We’re going back to the days of Simon & Garfunkel and other ‘70s folk rock duos, as country sweetheart Ashley Campbell and up-and-coming retro crooner Peedy Chavis lend their sweet harmonies to our version of KT Tunstall’s 2004 hit, “Suddenly I See.”
